<p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/16/wTSx4mCb3Z6Dt7K.png" alt="image-20220715191654249" /></p>

\[F_n\overline{F}_n=nI\]

\[F_n^{-1}=\overline{F}_n/n\]

<p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/16/DdqEt9FH2ayjRih.png" alt="image-20220715222918563" /></p>

