<p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/16/QdmWDjti5SrNuZf.png" alt="image-20220715223447063" /></p>

\[\omega^2_n=\omega_m\]

\[\omega^{2jk}_n=\omega^{jk}_m\]

<p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/16/DQGop3YPVaEeIFW.png" alt="image-20220715223459219" /></p>

